se this information to evaluate your use of the website, to compile reports on website activity and to provide the website operator with other services relating to website and Internet use. The IP address transmitted by your browser in the context of Google Analytics is not merged with other Google data. You may refuse the use of cookies by selecting the appropriate settings on your browser, however please note that if you do this you may not be able to use the full functionality of this website. You can also prevent Google from collecting the data generated by the cookie and relating to your use of the website (including your IP address) and from processing this data by Google by downloading and installing the browser plug-in available under the following link. Regarding the discussion about the use of analysis tools with complete IP addresses, we would like to point out that this website uses Google Analytics with the extension \"_anonymizeIp()\" and therefore IP addresses are only processed further in abbreviated form in order to exclude direct personal reference.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff; color: #808080;\">chowkbazarbd.com is owned by Chowkbazar Digital Enterprise. All rights reserved.</span></p>', '<h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 6px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1c1e21;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\"><a style=\"color: #808080; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;\" href=\"http://chowkbazarbd.com/?fbclid=IwAR2q0n4801TyNremX30LordqPysHMQiI5AwyE0JY1u1cDza6T8-9kO_n9rE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;-U&quot;}\" data-lynx-mode=\"async\" data-lynx-uri=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchowkbazarbd.com%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2q0n4801TyNremX30LordqPysHMQiI5AwyE0JY1u1cDza6T8-9kO_n9rE&amp;h=AT2M4G6Le84QOxzU8dPM3gR63ZPV2-_koClbWcFg-euSXrkWb_bXuBLkwz_aAj8bwAXTlDnrSwWZOOsvgpyXZ8rK5-V884TJmSnFe_wiOPKDHtiD-_sQiiF7QawetaaRpiYEhTpg9LuXf7A