" border=\"0\"></noscript></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href=\"http://cndahong.en.alibaba.com/productgrouplist-219521124/Zipper_puller_slider_PVC_aglets.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"//sc01.alicdn.com/kf/HTB1rIWFIVXXXXcpaXXXq6xXFXXXV/200502064/HTB1rIWFIVXXXXcpaXXXq6xXFXXXV.jpg\" border=\"0\" data-src=\"//sc01.alicdn.com/kf/HTB1rIWFIVXXXXcpaXXXq6xXFXXXV/200502064/HTB1rIWFIVXXXXcpaXXXq6xXFXXXV.jpg\" data-alt=\"Flat Drawstring Garment Cord Lace With Metal Tips\" data-width=\"780\" data-height=\"226\" /><noscript><img src=\"//u.alicdn.com/js/5v/esite/img/img-placeholder.png\" alt=\"Flat Drawstring Garment Cord Lace With Metal Tips\" width=\"780\" height=\"226\" border=\"0\"></noscript>&nbsp;</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"ali-anchor-AliPostDhMb-qvszd\" style=\"padding-top: 8px;\" data-section=\"AliPostDhMb-qvszd\" data-section-title=\"Our certifications\">\r\n<div style=\"padding: 10px 0;\">\r\n<p><a href=\"http://cndahong.en.alibaba.com/productlist.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><noscript><img src=\"//u.alicdn.com/js/5v/esite/img/img-placeholder.png\" alt=\"Flat Drawstring Garment Cord Lace With Metal Tips\" ori-width=\"750\" ori-height=\"750\"></noscript></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"ali-anchor-AliPostDhMb-avujb\" style=\"padding-top: 8px;\" data-section=\"AliPostDhMb-avujb\" data-section-title=\"FAQ\">\r\n<div id=\"ali-title-AliPostDhMb-avujb\" style=\"padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ddd; color: #333; font-weight: bold; padding: 8px 10px; line-height: 12px;\">FAQ</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding: 10px 0;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>FAQ</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><strong>1) What are the main products&nbsp;in your Draw cord/Drawstrings/Pull Strings/Shoelaces Series?</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; </strong>&nbsp; There are :</p>\r\n<p><strong>-Braiding Series</strong><br />The supplier offers variable width braided shoelaces with creative patterns to be used for shoes and garments. The <br />laces can be easily modified to match patterns and/or textures.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>-Piece-dyed Series</strong><br />Flat piece-dyed shoelace, soft and does not loosen easily. It can be processed with sublimation printing or <br />reflective laminating.<br /><br /><strong>-Rubber String &amp; Waxed Shoelace Series</strong><br />Characters can be printed on the round, elastic rubber string to demonstrate brand quality. This shoelace has <br />level 3 &ndash; 3.5 color fastness.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>-Jacquard &amp; Webbing with broad &amp; narrow width series</strong></p>\r\n<p>The flat or round Jacquard shoelace can enhance brand value and its broad &amp; narrow width is visually appealing . <br />The width is adjustable with this lace.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>-Memory Series</strong><br />You can change the shape of drawcord, according to your preference, instead of letting it fall naturally. This <br />drawcord lace hybrid contains memory plastic so the drawcord can be twisted or bent, but won&rsquo;t break.<br /><br /><strong>-Embossing Press Series</strong><br />Company trademark or patterns can be pressed clearly and completely on shoelaces. Patterns are pressure <br />resistant and will not deform after washing.<br /><br /><strong>-Reflective Series</strong><br />DaHong has recently launched eight reflective champagne colors, which have the same brightness as silver with up <br />to 500CPL. Reflective and fashionable, the reflective cord lace can be applied to shoes and garments.<br /><br /><strong>-Eco-yarn Series</strong><br />DaHong uses two kinds of eco-friendly materials: natural and recycled materials. These laces are made from <br />recycled PET bottles.<br /><br /><strong>-Suedette Series</strong><br />The string, which looks and feels like leather, can be applied to leather shoes, sneakers, dress shoes and as <br />draw cord for garments. The Suedette lace has 1.3 &ndash; 1.5 times the anti-slip effect of a regular oval-shaped <br />shoelace (its anti-loosening strength is 2 &ndash; 2.5kg; regular oval&rsquo;s is 1.5kg).<br /><br /><strong>-Standard Oval Series</strong><br />The traditional oval lace has good tensile strength and high abrasion. The oval lace has a good anti-slip quality <br />and does not easily loosen.<br /><br /><strong>-Printed Shoelace &amp; Sublimation Printing Series</strong><br />Any shoelace can look more appealing with the company trademark or custom patterns printed on it.<br /><br /><strong>-Adjustable Drawcord for Buckles</strong><br /><br />Suitable for buckles of bags. Easy to loose and tight with round elastic cord.<br /><br /><strong>-Pull Strings for Backpacks</strong><br />The woven and braided strings are designed specifically for sports bags with waterproof and high abrasion. The <br />10mm woven string has colorful or reflective effects and can be used as decoration on backpacks.<br /><br /><strong>-Elastic Drawcord for Garments</strong><br />Highly flexible elastic strings can be applied to the parts of clothes that focus on function and comfort. <br />Elastic drawcord is available in various colors. The elastic drawcord has good color fastness when washed and can <br />be used in sleeves or in the hems.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>-No Tie Elastic Shoelace</strong><br />The reverse strength of the buckle prevents the shoelace from getting loose during vigorous exercise. The elastic <br />shoelace is cheaper and easier to use . Its buckle can endure at least 15kg of strength and is suitable for <br />children&rsquo;s shoes, athletics shoes, and golf shoes.<br /><br />To learn more about our shoelace, drawcord &amp; pull string capabilities visit our parent company&rsquo;s site</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>2)What is your advantage of your Draw cord/Drawstrings/Pull Strings/Shoelaces ?</strong><br />---Advantages: Complex designs with abundant colors and patterns create three-dimensional presentations on drawcords and shoelaces that are both functional and decorative. Endless combinations of colors and patterns available. For apparel, shoe and sporting goods markets. Different types of materials and treatments are available for industrial and medical markets.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>3)Can we use our own logo on Draw cord/Drawstrings/Pull Strings/Shoelaces&nbsp;?</strong><br />---Definitely you can. Pls contact with our sales person you contacted about your detailed request of your own logos. <br />We can meet your any demands.Any drawcord/drawstrings/shoelace can look more appealing with the company trademark or custom patterns printed on it.</p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>4) Can you make Draw cord/Drawstrings/Pull Strings/Shoelaces&nbsp; in our designs?</strong><br />---Definitely you can. We are making many Draw cord/Drawstrings/Pull Strings/Shoelaces&nbsp;&nbsp;in the special designs from our customers. We can meet your any demands.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- tangram:4450 begin--> <!-- tangram:4450 end--></div>', '500', 'pcs', 10, 22, 0, 'flat,lace,cord,garments,accessories', 82, 'Product Type', 'Cords, Laces', 'Material', '100% Polyester', 'Technics', 'Twisted', 'Length/Diameter', 'Customized', 'Use', 'Bags, Garment, Home Textile, Shoes, Packing', '2020-03-09 17:03:00', '2020-03-20 10:23:49'),
